| Metric | Target | Achieved |
|--------|--------|----------|
| Overall Accuracy | > 80% | âœ… 88% |
| F1-score (macro avg) | > 80% | âœ… 88% |
| Per-class Accuracy | > 75% | âœ… All classes met |

**Confusion Matrix and Classification Report available in notebook.**

